[SHORT DESC]
Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/flash_cannon">Flash Cannon</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/flash_cannon">Flash Cannon</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>The user gathers all its light energy and releases it at once. It may also lower the foe's Sp. Def stat.</p>